## Keys type

Get keys of T.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type Keys<T> = T extends readonly unknown[]
  ? // unknown[] extends readonly unknown[], but readonly unknown[] not extends unknown[]
    TupleKeys<T> extends infer K
    ? K extends keyof T
      ? K
      : never
    : never
  : keyof T
```
**References:** [TupleKeys](./types-kit.tuplekeys.md)

## Example


```ts
 interface Props {
   a?: number
   b: number
   c: number
 }

 // Expect: 'a' | 'b' | 'c'
 type PropKeys = Keys<Props>
```
